 business owners the tools they need to get online and grow. That unwavering focus is what’s helped us grow to over 400,000 Sellers & Buyers around the world. And we’re just getting started.” “Our Entrepreneurs are your neighbourhood foodstuff sellers, make-up artists, skin therapists, fashion designers, plumbers, graphic artists, food truckers, and all the small business owners that breathe life into our economy and enrich our communities. To make this new development readily available for our entrepreneurs, we ensured that the first year of creating a market space for your business on our website and app is free,” she added.  To enable commenting and other interactive features, please switch to the more advanced .